                MP.init();
                var mp_langLink = function () {
                    var langlinks = document.querySelectorAll('.langLink');
                    for (var i = 0; i < langlinks.length; i++) {
                        langlinks.item(i).onclick = function () {
                            MP.init();
                            var lang = this.getAttribute('data-lang');
                            var url = this.getAttribute('data-href');
                            var tSite = MP.tSite.replace(/(https?:\/\/|\/?$)/g, '');
                            url = url.replace(/(https?:\/\/|\/?$)/g, '');
                            MP.switchLanguage(tSite.search(url) != -1 ? MP.oSite : url, lang, true);
                            return false;
                        }
                    }
                };
                if (window.addEventListener) {
                    window.addEventListener('load', mp_langLink, false);
                } else if (window.attachEvent) {
                    window.attachEvent('onload', mp_langLink);
                }
            </script>

    function SetTab() {

        $("#findFlights").css("visibility", "visible");
        $("#flightStatus").css("visibility", "hidden");
        $("#checkIn").css("visibility", "hidden");
        $('#findFlights').addClass('active');
        $('#flightStatus').removeClass('active');
        $('#checkIn').removeClass('active');
        $('#liBookFlight').addClass('active');
        $('#liCheckin').removeClass('active');
        $('#liFlightStatus').removeClass('active');
        //$('#liBookFlight').attr('aria-selected', true);
        //$('#liCheckin').attr('aria-selected', false);
        //$('#liFlightStatus').attr('aria-selected', false);
        $('#liBookFlight').attr('aria-disabled', false);
        $('#liCheckin').attr('aria-disabled', true);
        $('#liFlightStatus').attr('aria-disabled', true);

        if (window.location.href.indexOf("flight-status") > -1) {
            $("#flightStatus").css("visibility", "visible");
            $("#findFlights").css("visibility", "hidden");
            $("#checkIn").css("visibility", "hidden");

            $('#findFlights').removeClass('active');
            $('#flightStatus').addClass('active');
            $('#checkIn').removeClass('active');

            $('#liBookFlight').removeClass('active');
            $('#liCheckin').removeClass('active');
            $('#liFlightStatus').addClass('active');

            //$('#liBookFlight').attr('aria-selected', false);
            //$('#liCheckin').attr('aria-selected', false);
            //$('#liFlightStatus').attr('aria-selected', true);
            $('#liBookFlight').attr('aria-disabled', true);
            $('#liCheckin').attr('aria-disabled', true);
            $('#liFlightStatus').attr('aria-disabled', false);
            $('#liFlightStatus').trigger('click');
            return;
        }
        if (window.location.href.indexOf("check-in") > -1 || window.location.href.indexOf("my-trip") > -1) {
            $("#flightStatus").css("visibility", "hidden");
            $("#findFlights").css("visibility", "hidden");
            $("#checkIn").css("visibility", "visible");

            $('#findFlights').removeClass('active');
            $('#flightStatus').removeClass('active');
            $('#checkIn').addClass('active');


            $('#liBookFlight').removeClass('active');
            $('#liCheckin').addClass('active');
            $('#liFlightStatus').removeClass('active');

            //$('#liBookFlight').attr('aria-selected', false);
            //$('#liCheckin').attr('aria-selected', true);
            //$('#liFlightStatus').attr('aria-selected', false);
            $('#liBookFlight').attr('aria-disabled', true);
            $('#liCheckin').attr('aria-disabled', false);
            $('#liFlightStatus').attr('aria-disabled', true);
            $('#liCheckin').trigger('click');
        }

    }

    $('#liBookFlight').click(function () {
        $("#findFlights").css("visibility", "visible");
        $("#flightStatus").css("visibility", "hidden");
        $("#checkIn").css("visibility", "hidden");
        $('#findFlights').addClass('active');
        $('#flightStatus').removeClass('active');
        $('#checkIn').removeClass('active');
        $('#liBookFlight').addClass('active');
        $('#liCheckin').removeClass('active');
        $('#liFlightStatus').removeClass('active');

        $('#liBookFlight').attr('aria-disabled', false);
        $('#liCheckin').attr('aria-disabled', true);
        $('#liFlightStatus').attr('aria-disabled', true);



    });
    $('#liCheckin').click(function () {
        $("#flightStatus").css("visibility", "hidden");
        $("#findFlights").css("visibility", "hidden");
        $("#checkIn").css("visibility", "visible");

        $('#findFlights').removeClass('active');
        $('#flightStatus').removeClass('active');
        $('#checkIn').addClass('active');


        $('#liBookFlight').removeClass('active');
        $('#liCheckin').addClass('active');
        $('#liFlightStatus').removeClass('active');

        //$('#liBookFlight').attr('aria-selected', false);
        //$('#liCheckin').attr('aria-selected', true);
        //$('#liFlightStatus').attr('aria-selected', false);
        $('#liBookFlight').attr('aria-disabled', true);
        $('#liCheckin').attr('aria-disabled', false);
        $('#liFlightStatus').attr('aria-disabled', true);
    });
    $('#liFlightStatus').click(function () {
        $("#flightStatus").css("visibility", "visible");
        $("#findFlights").css("visibility", "hidden");
        $("#checkIn").css("visibility", "hidden");

        $('#findFlights').removeClass('active');
        $('#flightStatus').addClass('active');
        $('#checkIn').removeClass('active');

        $('#liBookFlight').removeClass('active');
        $('#liCheckin').removeClass('active');
        $('#liFlightStatus').addClass('active');

        $('#liBookFlight').attr('aria-disabled', true);
        $('#liCheckin').attr('aria-disabled', true);
        $('#liFlightStatus').attr('aria-disabled', false);


    });

    //  VSO 4657:   clear error validation on changing radio buttons
    //  Flight Status
    //  flight number radio button
    $('#byFlightNumber').click(function () {
        //  check if there is text before clearing
        if ($('#errorSummeryFromFS').text() != null) {
            $('#errorSummeryFromFS').hide();
        }
        //  check if there is text before clearing
        if ($('#errorSummeryToFS').text != null) {
            $('#errorSummeryToFS').hide();
        }
    });
    //  cities radio button
    $('#byCities').click(function () {
        //  check if there is text before clearing
        if ($('#errorSummeryFlightNumber').text() != null) {
            $('#errorSummeryFlightNumber').hide();
        }
    });
    //  Search button
    $('#btnFlightStatus').click(function () {
        //  check the radio button is 'checked'
        //  flight number
        if ($('#byFlightNumber').prop('checked')) {
            //  check that the flight number has been populated
            //  if not, re-display the error
            if ($('#flightScheduleSearch.FlightNumber').text() == '') {
                $('#errorSummeryFlightNumber').show();
            }
        }
        //  by cities
        if ($('#byCities').prop('checked')) {
            //  check for values
            if ($('#originFS').text() == '') {
                $('#errorSummeryFromFS').show();
            }
            else if ($('#destinationFS').text() == '') {
                $('#errorSummeryToFS').show();
            }
            else if (($('#originFS').text() == '') && ($('#destinationFS').text() == '')) {
                $('#errorSummeryFromFS').show();
                $('#errorSummeryToFS').show();
            }
        }
    });
</script>
